Context:
The text provides information about a pre-recorded information session for the Business Administration – Human Resources Program (with work experience) B154 at George Brown College. Interested individuals can sign up to learn more about the program, future career options, and receive updates about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more. The session can be attended from the comfort of one's desk.

Contact information for inquiries includes a phone number (416-415-2000) and a TTY number (1-877-515-5559), as well as an email address (ask.george@georgebrown.ca). The text also mentions visiting the college's Social Media Hub for further information. It is important to note that the information contained in the website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
